  { kanji:"食中毒 / 熱中症", kana:"しょくちゅうどく / ねっちゅうしょう", arti:"Keracunan makanan / Heat stroke", kat:"Penyakit & Gejala" },
  { kanji:"アレルギー / 痛み / 嘔吐", kana:"アレルギー / いたみ / おうと", arti:"Alergi / Sakit / Muntah", kat:"Penyakit & Gejala" },
  { kanji:"片麻痺 / 拘縮 / 骨折", kana:"かたまひ / こうしゅく / こっせつ", arti:"Lumpuh sebelah / Kontraktur / Patah tulang", kat:"Penyakit & Gejala" },
  { kanji:"下痢 / 便秘 / 脱水", kana:"げり / べんぴ / だっすい", arti:"Diare / Sembelit / Dehidrasi", kat:"Penyakit & Gejala" },
  { kanji:"発熱 / 発汗 / 発作 / 咳", kana:"はつねつ / はっかん / ほっさ / せき", arti:"Demam / Berkeringat / Kejang / Batuk", kat:"Penyakit & Gejala" },
  { kanji:"しびれる / むくむ / めまい", kana:"しびれる / むくむ / めまい", arti:"Kesemutan / Bengkak / Pusing", kat:"Penyakit & Gejala" },
  // Posisi & Postur
  { kanji:"仰臥位 (あおむけ)", kana:"ぎょうがい", arti:"Posisi telentang", kat:"Posisi & Postur" },
  { kanji:"側臥位 (よこむき)", kana:"そくがい", arti:"Posisi miring", kat:"Posisi & Postur" },
  { kanji:"腹臥位 (うつぶせ)", kana:"ふくがい", arti:"Posisi tengkurap", kat:"Posisi & Postur" },
  { kanji:"端座位 / 椅子座位 / 立位", kana:"たんざい / いざい / りつい", arti:"Duduk di tepi kasur / Duduk di kursi / Berdiri", kat:"Posisi & Postur" },
  { kanji:"体位 / 体位変換", kana:"たいい / たいいへんかん", arti:"Posisi tubuh / Mengubah posisi tubuh", kat:"Posisi & Postur" },
  { kanji:"姿勢", kana:"しせい", arti:"Sikap tubuh / Postur", kat:"Posisi & Postur" },
];

const EMOJI_MAP = {
  "Eliminasi & Kebersihan": "🚿",
  "Perawatan Diri & Mulut": "🪥",
  "Makanan & Minuman": "🍱",
  "Mobilitas & Alat Bantu": "♿",
  "Penyakit & Gejala": "🏥",
  "Posisi & Postur": "🛏️"
};

let deck = [];
let masteredSet = new Set();
let currentIndex = 0;
let isFlipped = false;
let filterMode = 'all'; // 'all' or 'unmastered'

function getFiltered() {
  const cat = document.getElementById('categoryFilter').value;
  let cards = cat === 'all' ? [...RAW_DATA] : RAW_DATA.filter(c => c.kat === cat);
  if (filterMode === 'unmastered') {
    cards = cards.filter(c => !masteredSet.has(cardKey(c)));
  }
  return cards;
}

function cardKey(c) { return c.kanji + '|' + c.kat; }

function buildDeck() {
  deck = getFiltered();
  currentIndex = 0;
  isFlipped = false;
  render();
}

function shuffleCards() {
  deck = getFiltered();
  for (let i = deck.length - 1; i > 0; i--) {
    const j = Math.floor(Math.random() * (i + 1));
    [deck[i], deck[j]] = [deck[j], deck[i]];
  }
  currentIndex = 0;
  isFlipped = false;
  render();
}

function showOnlyUnmastered() {
  filterMode = filterMode === 'unmastered' ? 'all' : 'unmastered';
  document.querySelector('[onclick="showOnlyUnmastered()"]').textContent =
    filterMode === 'unmastered' ? '📂 Tampilkan Semua' : '🎯 Belum Hafal Saja';
  buildDeck();
}

function resetMastered() {
  masteredSet.clear();
  filterMode = 'all';
  document.querySelector('[onclick="showOnlyUnmastered()"]').textContent = '🎯 Belum Hafal Saja';
  buildDeck();
}

function updateStats() {
  const cat = document.getElementById('categoryFilter').value;
  const allInCat = cat === 'all' ? RAW_DATA : RAW_DATA.filter(c => c.kat === cat);
  const masteredInCat = allInCat.filter(c => masteredSet.has(cardKey(c))).length;
  const total = deck.length;
  const mastered = deck.filter(c => masteredSet.has(cardKey(c))).length;

  document.getElementById('totalCount').textContent = total;
  document.getElementById('masteredCount').textContent = masteredInCat;
  document.getElementById('remainCount').textContent = total - mastered;

  const pct = total > 0 ? Math.round((masteredInCat / allInCat.length) * 100) : 0;
  document.getElementById('progressFill').style.width = pct + '%';
}

function render() {
  const area = document.getElementById('cardArea');
  updateStats();

  if (deck.length === 0) {
    area.innerHTML = `<div class="empty-state">
      <div class="emoji">🎉</div>
      <h3>Tidak ada kartu</h3>
      <p>Semua kartu sudah dihafal atau tidak ada kartu di kategori ini.<br>Coba reset hafalan atau ganti filter.</p>
    </div>`;
    return;
  }

  // All mastered in deck — show completion
  const allMastered = deck.every(c => masteredSet.has(cardKey(c)));
  if (allMastered && filterMode !== 'unmastered') {
    area.innerHTML = `<div class="completed-state">
      <div class="emoji">🏆</div>
      <h3>Semua Kartu Hafal!</h3>
      <p>Hebat! Kamu sudah hafal semua ${deck.length} kartu di sesi ini.</p>
      <button class="btn btn-teal" onclick="resetMastered()" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;padding:14px">↩️ Mulai Ulang</button>
    </div>`;
    return;
  }

  if (currentIndex >= deck.length) currentIndex = deck.length - 1;
  if (currentIndex < 0) currentIndex = 0;

  const card = deck[currentIndex];
  const isMastered = masteredSet.has(cardKey(card));
  const emoji = EMOJI_MAP[card.kat] || '📌';

  area.innerHTML = `
    <div class="flashcard-wrap" onclick="flipCard()" id="flashcardWrap">
      <div class="flashcard-inner ${isFlipped ? 'flipped' : ''}" id="cardInner">
        <div class="flashcard-face card-front ${isMastered ? 'mastered-card' : ''}">
          <span class="card-category-badge">${emoji} ${card.kat}</span>
          <div class="kanji-main">${card.kanji}</div>
          ${isMastered ? '<div class="mastered-tag">✓ Hafal</div>' : ''}
          <span class="card-hint">ketuk untuk lihat jawaban</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flashcard-face card-back">
          <span class="card-category-badge">${emoji} ${card.kat}</span>
          <div class="kana">${card.kana}</div>
          <div class="meaning">${card.arti}</div>
          <div class="category-label">${card.kat}</div>
          <span class="card-hint">ketuk untuk balik</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="nav-row">
      <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="prevCard()">← Prev</button>
      <div class="counter">${currentIndex + 1} / ${deck.length}</div>
      <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="nextCard()">Next →</button>
    </div>

    <div class="action-row">
      <button class="btn ${isMastered ? 'btn-danger' : 'btn-sage'}" onclick="toggleMastered()">
        ${isMastered ? '↩️ Batal Hafal' : '✅ Sudah Hafal'}
      </button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="nextCard()">⏭ Lewati</button>
    </div>
  `;

  // animate
  const wrap = document.getElementById('flashcardWrap');
  if (wrap) wrap.classList.add('card-animate');
}

function flipCard() {
  isFlipped = !isFlipped;
  const inner = document.getElementById('cardInner');
  if (inner) {
    inner.classList.toggle('flipped', isFlipped);
  }
}

function nextCard() {
  isFlipped = false;
  currentIndex = (currentIndex + 1) % deck.length;
  render();
}

function prevCard() {
  isFlipped = false;
  currentIndex = (currentIndex - 1 + deck.length) % deck.length;
  render();
}

function toggleMastered() {
  const card = deck[currentIndex];
  const key = cardKey(card);
  if (masteredSet.has(key)) {
    masteredSet.delete(key);
  } else {
    masteredSet.add(key);
    // auto-advance after marking mastered
    setTimeout(() => {
      isFlipped = false;
      if (filterMode === 'unmastered') {
        deck = getFiltered();
        if (currentIndex >= deck.length) currentIndex = Math.max(0, deck.length - 1);
      } else {
        currentIndex = (currentIndex + 1) % deck.length;
      }
      render();
    }, 400);
    updateStats();
    return;
  }
  render();
}

// Category filter change
document.getElementById('categoryFilter').addEventListener('change', () => {
  buildDeck();
});

// Keyboard navigation
document.addEventListener('keydown', e => {
  if (e.key === 'ArrowRight') nextCard();
  else if (e.key === 'ArrowLeft') prevCard();
  else if (e.key === ' ') { e.preventDefault(); flipCard(); }
  else if (e.key === 'Enter') toggleMastered();
});

// Init
buildDeck();
</script>
</body>
</html>
